name: 艾丽克丝·格施温德
name_full: 艾丽克丝·格施温德 Alex Geschwind

last_movies.title: 无耻之徒(美版) 第七季

introduction: Alex began dancing at the age of four and appeared in many shows associated with The Commonwealth Opera, Hampshire Performing Arts and the Pioneer Arts Center of Easthampton. She moved to Los Angeles at 16 with her family and finished her senior year at Hollywood High's performing arts magnet. Alex currently resides in Brooklyn, NY.
